{
  "stem": "9702.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Until we got a permit that we can take her, she died.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe better, so she didn't have to go through all that, that we went through later when people, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Better to die in your own bed than to be killed by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you-- she's buried in--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Druzkopol.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- I never saw my mother's grave.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The, the, the day of the burial-- it must have been Sunday-- I got very bad pain, stomach pains.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At that time I didn't know what it is.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But such a pain, that I couldn't even be at the levaya.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But later life, I knew what it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was gall-- my first gall bladder attack.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "By 17, I had a gall bladder attack.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then, we were there by my-- with our family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But then my mother had a brother in Sienkiewiczowka.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Sienkiewiczowka was much easier.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "These-- Druzkopol was surrounded with Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Ukrainian, this-- they were the worst.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were worse than the Germans because they knew every-- whoever is a Jew.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And any little thing, they killed right away, and slaughtered, and took away everything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know, every time they came out, with-- you give them gold.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You give them the furs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And, you know, you couldn't-- a Jew couldn't have anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Had to give them all away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my, my uncle-- my mother's brother that lived in Sienkiewiczowka-- got a permit for us to come to live with them, because he knew we are near the Czechish people, would be easier for us.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So middle of the night, one night, my father, my two brothers, and myself left Druzkopol.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we went-- I don't know-- it must have took about 7, 8 hours.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had a Ukrainian that we paid.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
